leads.lead_text: Leaves simple, linear or narrowly elliptic or obovate; flowers 4–6 mm diam., usually bisexual; petals absent; pericarp subwoody; north-western Victoria
Leaves pinnate, leaflets elliptic-oblong to elliptic-ovate; flowers 2–3 mm diam., usually unisexual; petals present but minute; pericarp thin; East Gippsland
